Package: dux
Version: 0.2.1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.34)
Maintainer: dux maintainers <root@localhost>
Description: persistent realtime disk usage + file search
 dux is an indexed, persistent du/ncdu with fast trigram file-name search
 and an optional live fanotify daemon. It answers "largest dirs/files",
 "fastest-growing paths", inode-usage, and deleted-but-open queries in
 milliseconds, and shows df-style filesystem capacity. Companion to xtop.
